game_description: Monkey Mischief is a multiplayer VR game for Meta Quest there are multiple maps such as Forest, Cave and A creepy horror map with Ai. the best part is there is a color changer and a custom username system. and Explore the map with friends in this party like game! A relaunch of my old game Chump Chimps. This game is heavily inspired by gorilla tag. This product is not affiliated with Gorilla Tag or Another Axiom LLC and is not endorsed or otherwise sponsored by Another Axiom LLC.
